{"title":"[加密]caesar cipher","date":"2020-01-30T08:40:01.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 30, 2020","L":"01/30/2020","MM-DD":"01-30"},"link":"2020/01/30/caesar cipher","tags":["JS","W3HEXSCHOOL","密碼學"],"updated":"2020-06-18T16:55:19.383Z","content":"<html><head></head><body><p>…</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h1 id=\"caesar-cipher-凱薩加密\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/30/caesar cipher#caesar-cipher-凱薩加密\"></a>caesar cipher(凱薩加密)</h1>\n<h2 id=\"原理\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/30/caesar cipher#原理\"></a>原理</h2>\n<p>在密碼學中，<strong>caesar cipher</strong>為一種最為人所知的加密方法，主要是利用<mark><strong>字元之間的偏移</strong></mark>來加密。</p>\n<p>而之所以叫凱薩加密，主要是因為據稱當年凱撒曾用此方法與其將軍們進行聯繫。</p>\n<p>在現今主要用於更複雜加密中的其中一個環節，ex:<strong>Vigenere Cipher(主要利用重複性與偏移來加密</strong>)等等</p>\n<p><strong>破解方法</strong>：主要利用Exhaustive attack（列舉法）來破解</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>下圖為caesar cipher的原理</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zdR7tjO.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<ol>\n<li>假設你輸入的密碼是<strong>ABCDE</strong></li>\n<li>輸入的偏移量是<strong>3</strong></li>\n<li>加密後的結果就會是<strong>DEFGHI</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"實作-JS\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"2020/01/30/caesar cipher#實作-JS\"></a>實作(JS)</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>請使用者輸入加密字串與偏移量</li>\n<li>將字串進行字元切割並存於array</li>\n<li>將字元進行<strong>ASKII table</strong>查表並且分類大小寫</li>\n<li>進行<mark><strong>字元偏移</strong></mark>（<strong>重要！！</strong>）</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>case1:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>輸入A(table:65)->偏移量3</li>\n<li>進行運算：65-65+3=3</li>\n<li>3+65=68->查表(D)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>case2:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>輸入Z(table:90)->偏移量3</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>進行運算：90-65+3=28</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>28/26=1…<strong>2</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>2</strong>+65=67->查表（C）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>下圖為</strong><mark> <a href=\"http://www.asciitable.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>ASKII table</strong></a></mark></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qZy9UaV.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>主要查表的JS語法如下：</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> c;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">var</span> b;</span><br><span class=\"line\">c = <span class=\"string\">'Aao'</span>.charCodeAt(<span class=\"number\">0</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//把字串Aao的A利用查ASCII的值存取到C</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">b = <span class=\"built_in\">String</span>.fromCharCode(<span class=\"number\">65</span>, <span class=\"number\">97</span>, <span class=\"number\">111</span>)<span class=\"comment\">//查詢ASCII表中的65 97 111 值存取到b</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`顯示答案<span class=\"subst\">${c}</span>`</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">`顯示答案<span class=\"subst\">${b}</span>`</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KNzLIgC.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n</body></html>","prev":{"title":"[型別區分]何謂強弱型別","link":"2020/02/05/typeoflang"},"next":{"title":"[框架設計]MVC","link":"2020/01/29/MVC"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/01/30/caesar cipher/","toc":[{"title":"","id":"caesar-cipher-凱薩加密","index":"1","children":[{"title":"","id":"原理","index":"1.1"},{"title":"","id":"實作-JS","index":"1.2"}]}]}